Class Serial

  • java.lang.Object
    • Serial
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<Paper>

    public class Serial
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<Paper>
    Project #2 CS 2334, Section 011 9/19/2013

    This class represents a serial publication. It is comprised of an ArrayList of Papers.

    Version:
    1.0
